---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Taxi Alternative Les 2 Alpes | Private VTC Grenoble | ShipCars"
    description="Book your VTC as a taxi alternative for Les Deux Alpes from Grenoble. Private driver, fixed price, all-comfort electric vehicle with space for skis. The most serene transfer to the resort.">

    <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1><strong>Taxi Alternative</strong> for Les Deux Alpes</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Your <strong>private VTC driver</strong> for a direct and secure transfer from Grenoble, without the constraints of a taxi.</p>
            <a href="/en/#booking" class="cta-button">Book my VTC for Les 2 Alpes</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="container text-container">
            <h2>Reach Les 2 Alpes Easily with a Reliable Taxi Alternative</h2>
            <p>
                The journey between <strong>Grenoble and the Les Deux Alpes resort</strong> is known for its mountain road. For a stress-free trip, ShipCars offers a <strong>taxi alternative</strong> that combines comfort, safety, and punctuality. No more waiting and fare uncertainty: your <strong>private driver</strong> will take charge of you for a door-to-door service.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">The Unique Advantages of your <strong>VTC Transfer</strong></h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">üèîÔ∏è</div>
                    <h3><strong>Safety</strong> on the Oisans Roads</h3>
                    <p>
                        Your <a href="/en/about"><strong>experienced driver</strong></a> perfectly masters the roads leading to Les 2 Alpes. Our <a href="/en/vehicle"><strong>electric vehicle</strong></a> is equipped for winter, guaranteeing you a journey in complete safety.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">üéø</div>
                    <h3><strong>Guaranteed Space</strong> for your Equipment</h3>
                    <p>
                        Travel with your <strong>skis, snowboards, and suitcases</strong> without worry. Our large <strong>435-liter</strong> trunk and folding seats are designed to accommodate all your gear.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="icon">‚úÖ</div>
                    <h3><strong>Fixed Price</strong>: The Right Price, No Surprises</h3>
                    <p>
                        The price of your <strong>VTC Grenoble - Les Deux Alpes</strong> is agreed upon in advance. It's the promise of a controlled budget and a serene journey, a real <strong>alternative to the traditional taxi</strong>.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">How Your Trip Unfolds</h2>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <h4>Average Travel Time</h4>
                    <p>Expect about <strong>1h15 to 1h30</strong> of travel time between Grenoble center and the Les Deux Alpes resort, depending on traffic and weather conditions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <h4>Tailored Pickup</h4>
                    <p>We pick you up at the address of your choice: Grenoble station, home, hotel... and drop you off directly at your accommodation in Les 2 Alpes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/en/ski-resort-transfers" class="secondary-button">See all our ski destinations</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to ski? Let us drive.</h2>
            <a href="/en/#booking" class="cta-button">Book my VTC Grenoble ‚Üî Les 2 Alpes</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    :root { 
        --accent: #35c2b5; 
        --dark-bg: #2d3a4c;
        --light-bg: #f8f9fa;
        --text-color: #333;
    }
    .page-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605540105435-9635b1b702b3?q=80&w=1974&auto=format&fit=crop') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        color: white;
        padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .page-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2em, 5vw, 3.5em); text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7); color: white; }
    .page-hero .subtitle { font-size: 1.2em; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 700px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem auto; }
    
    .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
        background-color: var(--accent); 
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px; 
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .content-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .text-container { max-width: 800px; text-align: center; margin: 0 auto; }
    .text-container h2, .section-title { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--dark-bg); text-align: center; font-size: 2.2em; }
    .text-container p { font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7; color: #555; }

    .features-section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .features-section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
    .feature-card {
        background: white;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        text-align: center;
    }
    .feature-card .icon { font-size: 2.5em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .feature-card h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--dark-bg); }
    .feature-card p { color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }
    .feature-card a { font-weight: bold; color: var(--accent); }

    .info-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) { .info-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
    .info-item {
        background: white;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .info-item h4 { font-size: 1.3em; color: var(--accent); }

    .secondary-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
        border: 2px solid var(--dark-bg);
        color: var(--dark-bg);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    /* ERREUR CORRIG√âE : Le "s" a √©t√© supprim√© */
    .secondary-button:hover {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        color: white;
    }

    .cta-section {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        /* ERREUR CORRIG√âE : "section" a √©t√© supprim√© */
        color: white;
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-section h2, .cta-section p { color: white; }
    .cta-section h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; } /* J'ai ajout√© un margin-bottom pour espacer */
    .cta-section p { max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem auto; opacity: 0.9; }

    .bg-light { background-color: var(--light-bg); }
    .bg-light .text-container p, .bg-light .feature-card p { color: #333; }
    .text-center { text-align: center; }
    .mt-4 { margin-top: 2rem; }
</style>